  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic and cook until fragrant, 1 minute.",
    "Add fideo and cook, stirring frequently, until lightly toasted, 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add smoked paprika and cayenne pepper, stir for 30 seconds.",
    "Deglaze with port wine vinegar and beef broth, scraping up browned bits from the bottom of the pan.",
    "Add butter and stir until melted.",
    "Stir in parmesan cheese until melted and well combined.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Warm lotus leaf wraps according to package instructions.",
    "Spoon fideo mixture into the center of each warmed lotus leaf, top with parsley.",
    "Fold the lotus leaf over the filling to form a wrap, and serve immediately."
  ],
